page.title: 12A Day in My Life(Felixstowe)
page.content: I get up at{6.00am}on school days and go for a run before breakfast.For that I like 2 weetabix with milk,and fruit juice.I change and go to school at 9am.We have maths,science,language work,art,craft,games during the days. We have a 15 minute break in the morning and afternoon.I have packed lunch which consists of 4 meat or cheese sandwhichs with brown bread and some fruit.School ends at 3.30.I go home and change into play clothes and go out to play with my friends. About{7.00pm}we have our tea.I like curry and rice best but we might have meat and potatoes or salad.I watch some television,then get ready for bed at 9.00pm and go to bed about 10.00pm.
